		</div>
		<div class="col-2">
			<p>
				At the start of this exercise, I looked up on several phone bills and talked to several people to understand various use cases and their frustrations with the phone bills they were receiving.
			</p>
			<p>Following that, I made the following assumptions to reduce the scope of the design:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>This is a dashboard for an individual who is subscribed to a family plan.</li>
				<li>This phone bill is to be viewed any time during the billing cycle.</li>
				<li>This plan does not have rollover minutes.</li>
				<li>This plan does not have unlimited free messages.</li>
			</ul>
			<p>During the design process, I conducted informal testing with some users and iterated based on feedback.</p>
		</div>

