			<h1>3 - Mid Fi</h1>
			<p>I briefly considered the value of organizing call history into two containers, one displaying longest calls and the other displaying the most called numbers.</p>

			<p>Initially I thought being able to visualize trends of cost would be useful, but I eventually removed it. I felt trends in usage amount over several months may be visually interesting, but do not provide enough information to act on. Also, phone bills tend to cost similar amounts across each month as well.</p>

			<p>Lastly, considering this should be scalable to mobile, complex charts are a challenge to display and interact with on mobile devices due to space constrains.</p>
